edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.utils

Class ValuesMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.json.JSONObject
      • edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.utils.ValuesMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.interfaces.Summarizable

    public class ValuesMap
extends JSONObject
implements edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.interfaces.Summarizable
    This is the key / value representation for keys and values when we are manipulating them in memory. This class also has some code that supports backwards compatability with older code. In particular, in some older code result values are always a list.
    Author:
    westy

        public boolean writeToValuesMap(ValuesMap destination)
